{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77fbfb53-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460lll–41"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"460lll–41"},"text":"§ 460lll–41.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Effective date of transfer","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Effective on October 1 of the first fiscal year for which Congress does not appropriate to the Tennessee Valley Authority at least $6,000,000 for the Recreation Area, or, if this Act is enacted during a fiscal year for which Congress has not made such an appropriation, effective as of ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-21"},"text":"October 21, 1998","children":[],"tail":", administrative jurisdiction over the Recreation Area is transferred from the Tennessee Valley Authority to the Secretary."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77fbfb54-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/277/dA/s101/e/tV/s541"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–277, div. A, § 101(e) [title V, § 541]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2681-231"},"text":"112 Stat. 2681–231","children":[],"tail":", 2681–318.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77fbfb55-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77fbfb56-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77fbfb57-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/277/dA/s101/e"},"text":"section 101(e) of div. A of Pub. L. 105–277","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2681-231"},"text":"112 Stat. 2681–231","children":[],"tail":", which enacted the Department of the Interior and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 1999. Title V of the Act, known as The Land Between the Lakes Protection Act of 1998, is classified generally to this subchapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
